               <head>Poems by Vaḥshī</head>
               <msContents>
                  <summary>1 copy of a work by Vaḥshī</summary>
                  <msItem class="https://lccn.loc.gov/sh89005046" n="1" xml:id="Uk_Delhi_Persian_1368B-item1">
                     <textLang mainLang="fa" otherLangs="ar">Persian and Arabic</textLang>
                     <note>
                        <p>Untitled collection of lyrics or ghazalīyāt in alphabetic order by the poet, Kamāl al-Dīn Muḥammad Bāfiqī Kirmānī takhalluṣ Vaḥshī (d. 991/1583).</p>
                        <p>Defective at beginning, supplemented with later replacement leaves (ff. 1-6).</p>
                        <p>Defective at end.</p>
                        <p>Not dated at end. The original portion is datable to the seventeenth century.</p>
                        <p>Replacement leaves in rough nastaʿlīq, with original folios in minute calligraphic nastaʿlīq.</p>
                        <p>Annotations, corrections, and additions in margins, usually written obliquely.</p>
                        <p>Not foliated.</p>
                        <p>Lacking original binding.</p>
                        <p>Paper dust wrapper BEIC legal publication on Regulation XVI for 9 September 1817, 26 Bhadon 1224 Banglah era, 14 Bhadon 1224 faṣlī era, 17 Bhadon 1224 Vilāyatī era, 13 Bhadon 1874 samvat era, 26 Shavvāl 1232 hijrī era); partial watermarks (J WHATMAN, 1814); torn and stained.</p>
                        <p>Folios unbound; cropped, wormholes, later repairs.</p>
                        <p>Condition fragile.</p>
                     </note>
                     <author>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa-Latn-x-lc" key="ark:/81055/vdc_100164657051.0x000001 viaf_30738316">Vaḥshī</persName>
                        <persName xml:lang="fa" key="viaf_30738316">وحشى</persName>
                     </author>
                  </msItem>
